# Normalize line endings in the repo to LF; check out native. Keeps the Windows‚ÜímacOS move
# clean (no CRLF churn) and guarantees shell scripts stay LF so they run on macOS.
* text=auto
*.sh   text eol=lf
*.dart text
*.md   text
*.json text
*.yaml text
*.cmd  text eol=crlf
*.ps1  text eol=crlf

# Binaries ‚Äî never touch.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.ico binary
*.zip binary
*.onnx binary
*.bundle binary
